{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"71dd347756","title":"中共中央关于成立财经、政法、外事、科学、文教各小组的通知","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"780aa904a8","index":0,"year":1958,"month":6,"day":10,"articleId":"71dd347756"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d009250878","name":"聂荣臻","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3f46836350","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于成立财经、政法、外事、科学、文教各小组的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"5db12c292a","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区党委，国家机关各党组，党中央各部委，人民团体各党组，军委各部门：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"92b57c8be1","type":"paragraph","text":"党中央决定成立财经、政法、外事、科学、文教各小组。这些小组是党中央的，直隶中央政治局和书记处，向他们直接作报告。大政方针在政治局，具体部署在书记处。只有一个“政治设计院”，没有两个“政治设计院”。大政方针和具体部署，都是一元化，党政不分。具体执行和细节决策属政府机构及其党组。对大政方针和具体部署，政府机构及其党组有建议之权，但决定权在党中央。政府机构及其党组和党中央一同有检查之权。现将各组名单通知如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"eb977d7edb","type":"paragraph","text":"财经小组12人：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"da24fda96c","type":"paragraph","text":"组长  陈云","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"6d2d60b10f","type":"paragraph","text":"副组长  李富春  薄一波  谭震林","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"c8f4eb6209","type":"paragraph","text":"组员  李先念  黄克诚  邓子恢  聂荣臻  李雪峰  贾拓夫  王鹤寿  赵尔陆","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"0e18c9a4e0","type":"paragraph","text":"政法小组5人：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"c5503f5ab6","type":"paragraph","text":"组长  彭真","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"71dd347756"},{"id":"10f041c79b","type":"paragraph","text":"组员  董